          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>No More Surprise Medical Bills Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill establishes several requirements relating to billing practices for out-of-network services provided by certain health care providers (e.g., hospitals), including notice and consent requirements; specified providers must also comply with such requirements as a condition of Medicare participation.</p>]]></text>
